data.title: Revised Obituary Page
data.text:
Listed on this page are members whose death was reported in the club newsletter. In time I hope to build up a substantial number of obituary tributes but as yet have only managed to do 39, which are highlighted in blue with purple background. Several of these have been gleaned from tributes by other members which appeared in club programmes at the time the member commemorated died.

Therese O'Brien 1952 - 53. d. February 2015. I never knew Therese as an active walker. Having joined the club in 1952 - 53 perhaps she had hung up her walking boots by the time I became an active member in 1988. However I well remember her as a faithful supporter of the club "Christmas" Parties, held in recent years in January. Her smiling face will be sadly missed since she died in February 2015, R.I.P.
